summary:
Kara and her dog are waiting for you in their little House on the Prairie (of Skyrim!) to accompany you in the underworld of the Bosmers...

This small house is located near the Western Watchtower of Whiterun

A huge tree, 9 houses, 21 companions (18 Bosmers), unicorns, old horses, mushskeevers, mushspiders, mushrooms ..
descriptionHtml:
[b][color=#ff0000][size=5]WORLD TREE OF SKYRIM[/size][/color][/b] [color=#00ff00][b]version 5.2 [/b][/color]([color=#ff0000]The DLC Dragonborn is required [/color]-[b] [u]NO OTHER MOD NEEDED[/u] [/b]- The .esp has been cleaned with TESVEdit - This mod contains "Data" with 2 files: .esp + .bsa)


[i]*[color=#00ff00]Kara[/color] and her *German Shepherd are waiting for you in their little House on the Prairie (of Skyrim!) to accompany you in the underworld of the Bosmers …

Many old horses have escaped,[color=#00ff00] Areth Selas[/color] is running after ... can you help her ?[/i]


[b]A Huge Tree, 9 Houses, 21 Companions (18 Bosmers), Unicorns, Old Horses, Mushskeevers, Mushspiders, Mushrooms ... and More again!

With 7 kinds of Bosmer headdresses ![/b]

[url=https://www.casimages.com/img.php?i=18090110101516616015871954.jpg][img]https://nsm09.casimages.com/img/2018/09/01//18090110101516616015871954.jpg[/img][/url]

[i]*If you don't like "Stupid Dog" ("vanilla" comment !) you have this mod:[/i][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/21225/?] No More Stupid Dog Comments by TheWinterhawk[/url]

[img]https://i.imgur.com/laBt0yD.gif[/img]


[i][b]The Small House is located near the Western Watchtower of Whiterun...[/b][/i]


[size=4][b][color=#ff0000]HOUSES[/color] WITH [color=#00ff00]COMPANIONS[/color][/b][/size]


[color=#ff0000][b]Small House[/b][/color] with [color=#00ff00]Kara[/color] and his dog (Lucky the young German Shepherd)

[img]https://i.imgur.com/114cWbt.gif[/img]

[color=#ff0000][b]Tronc House[/b][/color] with [color=#00ff00]Thophor[/color], [color=#00ff00]Ciite[/color], [color=#00ff00]Iddrael[/color] and [color=#00ff00]Breimir
[/color]
In this house, [color=#ffff00]7 gateways to Markath, Riften, Falkreath, Windhelm, Solitude, Helgen and Karthwasten[/color]

[img]https://i.imgur.com/tkvq4cB.gif[/img]

[color=#ff0000][b]Champ House[/b][/color] with [color=#00ff00]Araene[/color] the alchemist

In this house, [color=#ffff00]one gateway to Winterhold[/color]

[img]https://i.imgur.com/Vq7o3eN.gif[/img]

[color=#ff0000][b]Balcon House[/b][/color] with [color=#00ff00]Niphriel[/color] the necro ranger (she summons a piece of her own soul in the form of an "echo" of herself)

In this house, [color=#ffff00]one gateway to Whiterun[/color]

[img]https://i.imgur.com/ha5IiTa.gif[/img]

[color=#ff0000][b]Gland House[/b][/color] with [color=#00ff00]Eloalas[/color] the merchant

In this house, [color=#ffff00]2 gateways to Rorikstead and Shor's Stone[/color]

[img]https://i.imgur.com/4lT0Mcr.gif[/img]

[color=#ff0000][b]Mushroom House[/b][/color] with [color=#00ff00]Elegost[/color] and [color=#00ff00]Thuriel[/color]

In this house, [color=#ffff00]5 gateways to Morthal, Riverwood, Ivarstead, Dragonbridge and Dawnstar [/color]

[img]https://i.imgur.com/iyKwJpt.gif[/img]

[color=#ff0000][b]Temple [/b][/color] with [color=#00ff00]Fitronor[/color] and [color=#00ff00]Teloneth[/color] the temple guardians

[url=http://www.casimages.com/img.php?i=18012208103616616015489214.jpg][img]http://nsm07.casimages.com/img/2018/01/22//18012208103616616015489214.jpg[/img][/url]

[color=#ff0000][b]Tree House[/b] [/color] with [color=#00ff00]Elena[/color]

[url=http://www.casimages.com/img.php?i=18012208131016616015489216.jpg][img]http://nsm07.casimages.com/img/2018/01/22//18012208131016616015489216.jpg[/img][/url]

[color=#ff0000][b]Igloo House[/b] [/color] with [color=#00ff00]Wynter[/color]

[url=http://www.casimages.com/img.php?i=18012208193516616015489220.jpg][img]http://nsm07.casimages.com/img/2018/01/22//18012208193516616015489220.jpg[/img][/url]


The other bosmers are in the World of the Tree: [color=#00ff00]Ancher[/color] the animals trainer and his mushskeevers (in the kiosk), [color=#00ff00]Thaeril[/color] and [color=#00ff00]Nyri[/color] with the unicorns, [color=#00ff00]Edorfinn[/color], [color=#00ff00]Katara[/color] and [color=#00ff00]Limwen[/color]

[img]https://i.imgur.com/WxPSbp0.gif[/img]

[b][size=4][color=#ff0000]BOOKS/SPELLS[/color][/size][/b] To call upon creatures (old horses, unicorns, jellyfish, Echo a Bosmer, elves, dolphin, shark, mushspider)

Different bosmers and Farengar have these books

You must place this .esp at the bottom of the list in the Data Files when you launch the game to obtain the 20 books from Farengar ...(Normally, this is done automatically)

To have the creatures you can buy the “Spell tome: XXXX”, at Farengar Secret-Fire in Dragonsreach (Whiterun) or with an other "Spell Vendor" (ex: Sybille Stentor in the Blue Palace in Solitude).

With the books, you have the spells...

[img]https://i.imgur.com/QTYHUIE.gif[/img]

[b][size=4][color=#ff0000]ARMIES OF CREATURES[/color][/size][/b]

This mod adds the ability to quickly incubate eggs with the fire of the forge, and quickly create a horde of Mushspider/Penguin/Jellyfish (5, 15, 50, MORE ? ...[color=#ff0000]ATTENTION with the freezes in your computer ![/color])

To obtain these eggs, simply bring the “Mushspider/Penguin/Jellyfish Egg” found in a chest to a forge and create the "Incubated Mushspider/Penguin/
Jellyfish Egg" in the "misc" section. Now open up your inventory, navigate to "Scrolls" and there they are. You throw them and when they hit the ground they hatch into Mushspider/Penguin/Jellyfish

When your creatures die, remember to loot their corpses for more eggs

Eloalas already sells eggs incubated

[img]https://i.imgur.com/ZLMJlNy.gif[/img]

[b][color=#ff0000][size=4]FOLLOWERS[/size][/color][/b]

You can talk with 11 Followers: 3 spriggans, a mushskeever, a penguin, and 6 mushrooms (Wait - Follow - Trade - Favor - Dismiss)

You can only have one follower at a time: if you want a different one, you need to dismiss the first one before you recruit them.

If you have any problem with the dialog box, or if telling the follower to return at home doesn't dismiss him, or if you have lost the active follower, you can try this:

Type “²” or "`" or "~" key to get into console, and type:

set playeranimalcount to 0

[img]https://i.imgur.com/TumyHP5.gif[/img]

[b][color=#ff0000][size=4]Bugs or problems[/size][/color][/b]

The dog does not bark in the small house (only), why ?

When you dismount (horse or unicorn) on a slope you can fall under the decor...

The mushskeever has trouble following Ancher but it always arrive

The companions are struggling to follow you on very steep slopes...but they always arrive

Unfortunately in the Tree House it will rain inside when it rains outside…
You have a mod that fixes it: [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/52612/?] Real Shelter [/url]
